Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 004—\NBall torn to pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wow…\N– Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{正確のスパイク}Such an accurate spike…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{丸で精密機会のようだわ}Almost like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. She's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{あなたは新しいキャプテンの、あいはらこずえさんね。}Are you the new captain,\NAyuhara Kozue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどり、みどりじゃないの？}Midori! Midori, is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{なか？}Naka? Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{ みどり、どうしたて言うの？}Midori, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日転校して来たの。}I've transferred today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{パパの会社この富士見市にも、\N????ことになったのよ。}My dad's company opened a new office here in Fujimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ。懐かしいわ。ね、何年ぶりかしら？}– Ah. Long time no see.\N– How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川みどりさんってね、小学校であたしたちと同じクラスだったのよ。}Hayakawa Midori-san and I were in the same class in the grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{五年生の時だったかな。}We were in the fifth class, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{確か母さんの方へ転校してたなけど、また戻って来たのね。}If I remember, she moved to her mom's place, but she returned now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san's family is in top management, so they're very rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{でもかっこよなくなバレー部に入ってると思わなかったわ。}Who would've think you'd enter a cool volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしは始めてばかりなの、まだだめよ。}I've just started, so I'm not any good yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{それにみどり、凄いじゃないの。今見てたわよ。}But you're something else, Midori. I could see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{あんな凄い一人バレー見たら始めてよ。}Really. It's my first time seeing someone this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{京都へ行ってから、ずっとバレーやってたの。}I've been playing ever since I went to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{でも、あの???ならあいはらさんだってできるわね。}But this much should be easy for Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、やってみなければ…}Well, I'd have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{できないはずないわよ。だって、こずえさんはキャプテンでしょ？}There's no way you couldn't do it. After all, Kozue-san, you're the captain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日からバレー部に出っていただくわ,キャプテンさん。}From now on, I'll be coming to the volleyball club, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{さ、練習よ。大会はもう直ぐなのよ。}Well, let's practice. The tournament's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ＯＫ}OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃね。}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしも明日から練習させてもらうわ。}I'll be coming to practice too from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、よろしく。}I hope we get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{おい！キャプテン！}Hey, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部の新キャプテン!}The volleyball club's new captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん！}Tsutomu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{あいはらくん、どうかしたのかい？なんだが、???にしているだけど。}Ayuhara-kun, did something happen? You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん、別に。}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{練習で疲れたのかい？}Tired from the practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{とうがいちく選手権大会のスケジュールは決まったんだろ。}The tournament's schedule was decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{新キャプテンあいはらこずえいながら、それでは困るじゃないか。}It'd be troublesome if the new captain Ayuhara Kozue wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{大会優勝目指して,絶対に頑張った貰わなくちゃ。}You have to do your best to win the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、努さん。なんだい？}– Hey, Tsutomu-san.\N– Hm? What it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん！}Tsutomu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さあん！}Tsutomu-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさんだ！}– It's Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{あの…商会しよう。}Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら。あいはらさん。}Oh. Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{なんだ。君たちもうしってたのか。}What, you know yourselves already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{え。あたしは今日バレー部に入ったの。キャプテンあいはらさんには、も挨拶にしたわ。}Yes. I entered the volleyball club today. I've already greeted captain Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうだったのか。}That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{努さん、あいはらさんと同じクラスでもないのに、中良い見たいのね。}Tsutomu-san, you're not in the same class as Ayuhara-san, but I feel you get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{ん。実は、僕達親戚なんだ。}Yeah. To tell you the truth, we're related.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{僕のおばさん、つまり僕の母さんの妹の結婚した相手が、あいはらくんのお父さんの弟。}My aunt, in other words my mom's younger sister, is married to Ayuhara-kun's father's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{つまり、叔父さんなんだ。分かる？}In short, her uncle. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょっと??しいけど、間違いない親戚なんだ。}It's a little roundabout, but we're most definitely relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:05:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら、そうなの？ね、あいはらさん。あたしと努さんは、幼児?からずっと一緒だったの。}Oh, that was it? Ayuhara-san, I've known Tsutomu-san ever since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{小学校で?????の、仲良し成ったのよ。}We became good friends at elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{みどりさんが京都に行くまえに、家が僕の家の近所だったんだよ。}Midori-san was my neighbor before she went to Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{ね、努さん。努さんの所へパパから???ちょうど良かったわ。一緒に行きましょう。}Hey, Tsutomu-san. I was about to deliver a welcome gift to your family from my papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{ちょうど良かったわ。一緒に行きましょう。}It's good that I met you here. Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{じゃ、さようなら。}We'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{さようなら。}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川みどりさんは転校してきた。}Hayakawa Midori-san has transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部に何が起こりそう気がする。}I feel that something's about to happen in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{バレー部に何が起こりそう気がする。}I hope I am thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:50.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,Fujimi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,Teachers room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{どもありがとうございました。}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{いあ。お父さんからわざわざ電話をいただく間でもなく、}No, no. After having received the call from your father…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{わたしも運動部に力を入れるべきだとは考えていたんだよ。}…I thought I should put an effort into the sport clubs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{まそれには先ずバレー部を強くすることだね。}Well, volleyball club comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{劣等生だと言われていたのグループの生徒達も少しずつ成績が割ってきてますわ。}The students who were said to be poor performing are slowly improving their grades too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{これもスポーツお始めたおかげでしょうね。}I guess this is thanks to the sports, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{そ。 それだけでも、スポーツと言うものが以下に大切ものか。 はっきりしている。}Indeed. This alone is enough to consider sports important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{学校はあくまで学力第一です。}The school is mostly about academic achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{しかしま、クラブ勝つどに、力を入れていくもいいでしょう。}But yes, putting effort into club victories should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{優勝でもしてくれれば、高名はげろことなりますからな。}If they do win, it might increase the school's prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best. We will certainly win the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{バイバイ、さようなら}– Bye bye!\N– See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{あら？皆どうしたのかしら。}Hm? I wonder where's everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{親分！じゃなくて、キャプテン！}Chief! I mean, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{どうしたの？皆、練習の時間だって言うのに。}What's the matter? It's practice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{今日からね、体育館で練習できるになったよね。}We can practice in the gym since today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？体育館で？}Huh? In the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{あたしたちのバレーの試合お見て、教頭先生や皆がはっと気づいたのよ。}After our match, the teachers and everyone have finally noticed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{これは運動部に力を入れるべきである。得に、バレー部にってさ！}They want to support sport clubs more. Especially the volleyball club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{ほんと？そよ。気がつく？おそいくらいよ。}– Really?\N– Yep. They're slow if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{といっても、本当はみどりが教頭先生に頼みこんだからなんだ。}But in reality, Midori has asked the head teacher for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hayakawa-san did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{—こっちに持ってきて。\N—うん。}– Leave them here.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さん、ありがとう。ここで練習できるなんて本当に素敵。}Thank you, Hayakawa-san. It's wonderful that we can practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{寒い天気外で練習する辛いもん。}We no longer need to worry about cold weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{はー早川さんで凄い力があるのね。}Ha-Hayakawa-san sure is powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{それはお金持ちだからよ。お金持ちには?}It's only natural when she's so rich. With wealth comes great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{そうか。でも早川さんはバレー部に入ってくるよかったわね。}R-Right. It's good that Hayakawa-san has joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここで練習できるし、それに早川さんのスパイクは凄いわね。}Not only we're able to practice here\h– her spike is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{早川さん、どもありがとう。}Thank you, Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？なんのこと？}Hm? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{ここ練習できること?}Ah, for being able to practice here? It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:08:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all for the victory in the tournament. Now, let's practice. You better do you best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{不要グループで有名だったそうじゃないの。 聞いたわよ。}I heard about your reputation of the "useless group".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{え？それは言わないでよ。耳が痛いわ。}– Huh?\N– Don't say that, it makes my ears hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an old story. We're different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! We're serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of the volleyball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Ever since we started playing—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for Ayuhara-san, you'd get expelled from the school, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way over the line. Who said it? I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that from Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,– Really?\N– Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, it's okay to be open about this. Haven't you told me it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We truly owe Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But expulsion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,– That's cruel.\N– Yes, it's just heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,– Don't get ahead of yourself!\N– Easy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let it be. You're here now, right? If we win the tournament, let's just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Stick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice time. Toss the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's… that's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ayuhara-san.\N– Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're such a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori was like that since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's wealthy, alone and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fujimi Academy hasn't won a match even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a team that is a capable of winning the upcoming tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I also think that we need a resolute captain. Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,– Of course.\N– Hayakawa-san would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. After all it's thanks to her that we can practice in a gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If Midori was the captain, we'd get far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some never saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think gathered us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Ayuhara-san did badmouth us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think our captain would do that? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori, what are you scheming? Stop being so egocentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you only think about yourself, you'll trip soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey, it's about time you said something!\N– Kashiwagi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But she…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign my role as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be the captain, but didn't ask the head teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thinking of the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Also it's not up to oneself to become or quit being a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a decision of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's skip the practice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself. You're the only one who can be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Our chief must be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than who is or isn't the captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,…I am afraid if Hayakawa-san will torn apart our club that we've just managed to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball is about team work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose to that selfish lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When captain has it together, everything works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up my love for volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a strong and elegant team as much as Hayakawa-san. No, I want it even more than her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hold it while I pull the other side.\N– Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Hayakawa-san, you don't need to do such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how good I am, I am still a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that I perform newcomers' tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san is so splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san never did such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because she's the captain. I am different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd do this even if I was the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After all when one loves volleyball, they're fine doing any important task.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Way better than Ayuhara-san ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, way better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are. I came all the way from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashiwagi-san is really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,People like Midori-san are restless since their childhoods until they're treated like a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But why does she want to become a captain so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be fine if I wasn't captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that. It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I could probably talk her out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it'd be better if you resolved it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With the tournament around the corner, it's the most important time for your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, new captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you found your purpose in the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you become like a balloon without air again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit the volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with the way you're now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have the patience for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if we had a fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball club will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why even if Hayakawa-san did become a captain, I'd still be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? There's no stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delivered directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san. I want to talk with you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please meet me at 7 AM at the volleball's club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Hayakawa-san is up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to lock the door yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized only this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if our equipment was stolen, and this is why I've asked you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it. I don't think anyone would steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be all right, but let's go and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,Volleyball club's room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It it's unlocked all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You come at the right moment. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,– Whoa.\N– How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The net is torn too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who hates volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This? It was lying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably used this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ayuhara-san, you're pretty dreadful person.\N– What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, you're holding a grudge against me, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, are you saying it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way any of us could destroy important equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished listening to our captain. Aren't you, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The title of captain doesn't fit Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed in you. I didn't think you're such a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, do you want to become the captain this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, just say so openly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resort to writing roundabout letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to pick a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I think it's clear that you don't deserve the title of captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am trying to do my best for the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,– Wow!\N– Brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These were all funded by Hayakawa-san's father. It sure is nice to be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With these we'll be able to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone decided that I'll be our new captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori, if you don't knock it off, I'm not going to tolerate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, don't you think that's too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's the decision of our members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It already has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, won't you be coming to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll trouble us if you don't listen to me from tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a strong team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, looks like you lost to Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Defeat doesn't suit you, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll endure it if it means improvement for the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,– Bu—\N– How far can you go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouze-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,– Kozue-chan.\N– Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've returned earlier today and you seem off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you feel unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good then. I got a call from Hayakawa-san's family today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to invite you to a dinner, Kozue-chan. They'll even send a car for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This way please. Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yeah.\N– Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Midori's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, where is Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be here in a second. Sit, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, it was me who called you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori became your captain. I hope you get along well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,– Uhm…\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, there's something I want to ask you as Midori's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to do your best under Midori from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show Midori to the world by putting her in the Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that Midori's true power goes unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If your volleyball club became Japan's best, Midori's fame would obviously rise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As a bonus, I'll buy each of you whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Volleyball isn't a place to make yourself popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're asking you to work hard so that Midori alone gets famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-san, I'll make myself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With your way of thinking, there's no way you'll get to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's go back.\N– Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say to offend her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I have to think of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She has some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she think volleyball is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped that if I persevered, everything will work out, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, I'm sorry. I have to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me who cut balls and the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'll be hard for us to get famous under Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I did it. It's very embarrassing and I regret it now. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to make up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of our club and the teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you forgive me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best on our way to the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I need Ayuhara Kozue-san's power for the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to playing, I'm the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll certainly become a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:24:00.58,Alternative,,0,0,0,,After Midori and Kozue called a truce, the coach Hongou…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:03.16,Alternative,,0,0,0,,…immediately begins a hard training.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:08.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,But the peace doesn't hold long and soon enough, a problem with staff members arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:12.27,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Even so, the coach continues with his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:19.04,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Under his guidance, Kouze and Midori's true rilvarly becomes ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:23.01,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.
